      "id": "https://balkaninsight.com/2017/12/05/romanian-ex-monarch-dies-aged-96-12-05-2017/",
      "title": "Romanian Ex-King Michael Dies Aged 96 | Balkan Insight",
      "url": "https://balkaninsight.com/2017/12/05/romanian-ex-monarch-dies-aged-96-12-05-2017/",
      "publishedDate": "2017-12-05T00:00:00.000Z",
      "author": "Ana Maria Luca",
      "text": "[![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2044%2044'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.facebook.com/balkaninsight/)\n\n[![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2044%2044'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://twitter.com/BalkanInsight?lang=en)\n\n[![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2044%2044'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.instagram.com/balkan_insight/?hl=en)\n\n[![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2045%2044'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.youtube.com/user/BirnTV)\n\n[![Balkan Insight](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://balkaninsight.com/)\n\nRomania’s last king, Michael I, died on Tuesday following a battle with cancer.\n\n| |\n| --- |\n| ![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E) |\n| Romania’s ex-king Michael I. Photo: familiaregala.ro |\n\nRomania’s former king, Michael I, passed away on Tuesday aged 96 at his residence in Versoix, near Geneva in Switzerland, following a battle with cancer, the royal family announced.\n\nMichael, 94, a cousin of Britain’s Queen Elizabeth and the last surviving head of state from World War II, [retired](https://balkaninsight.com/en/article/romania-s-ex-king-says-farewell-to-public-life-03-06-2016-1) from public life in spring 2016.\n\nThe eldest of his five daughters, Princess Margareta, who is the current custodian of the crown, [is next in line](https://balkaninsight.com/en/article/romania-royals-see-drama-as-ex-king-fades-11-10-2017) for the position of head of the Royal House.\n\nShe is followed by her sister, Princess Elena and her daughter, Elisabeta Karina.\n\nMichael became the monarch for the first time when he was only six years old, from 1927 to 1930, after his father, King Carol, briefly abdicated.\n\n- [Romania](https://balkaninsight.com/tag/romania/)\n\n#### BIRN\n\n[VIEW ALL POSTS](https://balkaninsight.com/author/birn/)\n\n[![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://balkaninsight.com/premium-subscription/?utm_source=Homepage&utm_medium=Website_banner&utm_campaign=Premium_Plus_banner_2019&utm_term=Premium_plus_banner&utm_content=Textlink)\n\n- [![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20160%20160'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://balkaninsight.com/2025/08/08/week-in-review-trials-tricksters-and-controversial-legacies/)\n\n- [![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20160%20160'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://balkaninsight.com/2025/08/08/constant-war-kosovos-documentary-festival-addresses-age-of-conflict/)\n\n- [![](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20160%20160'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://balkaninsight.com/2025/08/08/democracy-digest-nawrocki-signals-conflict-ahead-",
      "image": "https://balkaninsight.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/king-660.jpg",
