ia.org/wiki/Pele%C8%99_Castle), Sinaia, Romania |\n| Died | 5 December 2017(2017-12-05) (aged 96) [Aubonne](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aubonne), Switzerland |\n| Burial | 16 December 2017 Royal Cathedral, [Curtea de Argeș Monastery](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Curtea_de_Arge%C8%99_Cathedral), Curtea de Argeș, Romania |\n| Spouse | [Anne of Bourbon-Parma](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_of_Romania) ​ ​ (m.1948; died 2016)​ |\n| [Issue](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Issue_(genealogy)) | - [Margareta, Custodian of the Crown of Romania](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margareta_of_Romania) - [Princess Elena](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Princess_Elena_of_Romania) - Princess Irina - Princess Sophie - [Princess Maria](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Princess_Maria_of_Romania_(born_1964)) |\n| [House](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynasty) | - [Romania](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/House_of_Romania) (from 2011) - [Hohenzollern-Sigmaringen](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hohenzollern-Sigmaringen#Romanian_branch) (until 2011) |\n| ",
