      "text": "[![Familia Regală a României / Royal Family of Romania](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/wp-content/themes/imbalance2/images/logo-rr.png)](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/)\n\n![Caută](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/wp-content/themes/imbalance2/images/icon-search.svg)\n\n# His Majesty King Michael of Romania has died\n\n05.12.2017/ [Jurnal](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/category/jurnal/)/ [25 comentarii](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/www.romaniaregala.ro#comments)\n\n[Tweet](http://twitter.com/share)\n\n| |\n| --- |\n| ![](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Death-Announcement-King-Michael-of-Romania.jpg) [Tweet](http://twitter.com/share) |\n\n### 25 comentarii\n\n01. ![](https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b780b72d32d815871b4b57b884f07a3a01d6fe309fe6c6d548b7731d52862656?s=64&d=mm&r=g)Renato Barreto Mayrsays:\n\n\n\n [05.12.2017 at 15:09](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/#comment-259276)\n\n\n\n Traiasca in memoria noastră Regele MIHAI I !!!\n\n\n\n Traiasca Regina MARGARETA I !!!\n\n\n\n Here from distant BRASIL !!!\n\n\n\n ALL MY LOVE !!!\n\n\n\n [Reply](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/?replytocom=259276#respond)\n\n02. ![](https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87c6e56b7f667c9905013c8e0521fd22dff80760535a00977371115c9613aac4?s=64&d=mm&r=g)Ileana Crudusays:\n\n\n\n [05.12.2017 at 15:38](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/#comment-259284)\n\n\n\n Requiescat in pace, King Michael!\n A fost o onoare de a-i fi contemporani și o bucurie că i-am fost compatrioți.\n\n\n\n [Reply](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/?replytocom=259284#respond)\n\n03. ![](https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7c9c5847f03161b322d869f5f5ad7f2d20ed862529017edf86f5313551307330?s=64&d=mm&r=g)Tatjana Koprolsays:\n\n\n\n [05.12.2017 at 17:49](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/#comment-259334)\n\n\n\n To\n ROYAL FAMILY OF ROMANIA\n\n\n\n The news of His Majesty King Michael I of Romania death was very sadly received by us personally, and we send our sincere condolences.\n\n\n\n We hope the burden of your sadness will be lightened somewhat by the knowledge that millions of Romanian people and friends are grieving with You during this time of sorrow.\n\n\n\n Sincerely,\n\n\n\n Marcel Koprol & Tatjana\n Ambassador\n\n\n\n [Reply](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/?replytocom=259334#respond)\n\n04. ![](https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/57ae9b81b83000e8910c62f4829fac08cef5f3bf354c3de4e85df7be6377a57b?s=64&d=mm&r=g)[ANTONIA FRANGI](http://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/)says:\n\n\n\n [05.12.2017 at 22:35](https://www.romaniaregala.ro/jurnal/his-majesty-king-michael-of-romania-has-died/#comment-259402)\n\n\n\n riposi in pace servo di dio michele ultimo re di romania.\n Finalmente le sofferenze sonofinite e vostra maestà e libero, libero di riunirsi alla sua dev"
