e (archived 28 February 2013) Cycling - Road at the <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Summer</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span>. London2012","pageid":22290072,"wordcount":1019,"timestamp":"2025-07-06T18:10:19Z"},{"title":"Basketball at the 2012 Summer Olympics – Men's tournament","snippet":"The men&#039;s basketball tournament at the <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Summer</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> in London, began on 29 July and ended on 12 August, when the United States defeated Spain 107–100","pageid":31816529,"wordcount":495,"timestamp":"2025-07-08T12:30:55Z"},{"title":"Weightlifting at the 2012 Summer Olympics","snippet":"Weightlifting competitions at the <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Summer</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> in London were held from 28 July to 7 August in the ExCeL venue. Fifteen gold medals were awarded","pageid":31944084,"wordcount":829,"timestamp":"2025-05-02T18:56:03Z"},{"title":"India at the 2012 Summer Olympics","snippet":"India competed at the <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Summer</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> in London, from 27 July to 12 August <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span>. A total of 83 athletes, 60 men and 23 women, competed in 13 sports","pageid":28964743,"wordcount":1741,"timestamp":"2025-07-12T17:56:15Z"},{"title":"Athletics at the 2012 Summer Olympics","snippet":"24 April 2013) Athletics at the <span class=\"searchmatch\">2012</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Summer</span> <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> at SR/<span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> (archived) IAAF <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympics</span> webpage BBC Sport <span class=\"searchmatch\">Olympic</span> athletics website 51°32′19″N 0°00′59″W﻿","pageid":31560106,"wordcount":2831,"timestamp":"2025-07-14T12:59:49Z"},{"ti