e My Money\" (contains elements of \"Phresh Out the Runway\")\n\"Where Have You Been\" / \"Only Girl (In the World)\" (contains elements of \"Cockiness (Love It)\")\n\"We Found Love\" (contains elements of \"S&M\")\n\"Rude Boy\" (DJ Klean remix; contains elements of \"Kiss It Better\")\n\"Work\"\n\"Wild Thoughts\"\n\"Pour It Up\" (contains elements of \"Birthday Cake\", \"Numb\" and \"Pose\")\n\"All of the Lights\"\n\"Run This Town\"\n\"Umbrella\"\n\"Diamonds\"\n\n\n== References ==","sections":[]}],"categories":["Category:2023 in American music","Category:2023 in American television","Category:2023 in Arizona","Category:All Wikipedia articles written in American English","Category:Articles with short description","Category:CS1 Brazilian Portuguese-language sources (pt-br)","Category:CS1 maint: multiple names: authors list","Category:February 2023 in the United States","Category:Rihanna","Category:Short description is different from Wikidata","Category:Super Bowl halftime shows","Category:Television shows directed by Hamish Hamilton (director)","Category:Use American English from February 2023","Category:Use mdy dates from February 2023"],"links":["14th NFL Honors","1994 Green Bay Packers season","1994–1996 United States broadcast television realignment","1996 NFL season","1997 NFC Championship Game","1998 NFC Championship Game","1998 NFL season","2001 NFL season","2003 NFC Wild Card playoff game (Seattle–Green Bay)","2004 NFL season","2007 NFC Championship Game","2007 NFL season","2007 New England Patriots season","2008 Pro Bowl","2009 NFC Wild Card playoff game (Green Bay–Arizona)","2010 NFC Championship Game","2010 NFL season","2011 Pro Bowl","2013 Green Bay Packers–Dallas Cowboys game","2013 NFL season","2014 NFC Championship Game","2016 NFL season","2018 NFC Championship Game","2018 NFL draft","2018 NFL season","2019 NFC Championship Game","2019 NFC Divisional playoff game (Seattle–Green Bay)","2019 NFL season","2020 NFC Championship Game","2021 NFL season","20